Umunsi w' igiti mu Rwanda ni umunsi ngaruka mwaka wizihizwa hibandwa ku kamaro k' igiti mu mibereho ya muntu kandi ukaba n' umunsi washyizweho n' umuryango wabibumbye (UN) <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/umuryango-w-abibumbye-washimye-uko-u-rwanda-rukomeje-gutera-amashyamba</ref>

